Package wisedevil.credentials

This package contains classes to manage encrypted credentials.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICredentialDatabase
    Interface for the CredentialDatabase class.
    IKeyring
    Interface for the Keyring class.
    Password
    This interface provides access to generic password data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Credential
    Contains credential information.
    CredentialDatabase
    This class provide a facility for maintaining a database of credentials and keyrings.
    Keyring
    This class provides a pooling facility for related credentials.
    TextPassword
    This class contains text password information.
